      <T n="text">0xC6F30F3D<!--Your Sim can now master the art of <b><font color='#199C2C'>Tattooing</font></b>! Begin by purchasing a <b><font color='#199C2C'>Tattoo Table</font></b> to start tattooing other Sims, or buy a <b><font color='#199C2C'>Digital Sketchpad</font></b> to practice tattoo designs!\n\nTattooing is a 10-level skill, and with each level, your Sim learns new tattoo designs and earns more for their services! They can also learn and offer new tattooing services, such a <b><font color='#199C2C'>Tattoo Touchup</font></b> or a <b><font color='#199C2C'>Tattoo Removal</font></b>.--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InEP18\UI\Tutorial\EP18_Lesson_Tattooing_Slide2.png">2f7d0004:00000000:9fbd5d8c759554c0</T>
      <T n="text">0xBDB6C1D8<!--When you purchase a <b><font color='#199C2C'>Tattoo Table</font></b>, your Sim can offer a range of tattooing services!\n\nChoosing a normal tattoo allows you to select from premade designs, while offering a <b><font color='#199C2C'>custom tattoo</font></b> lets you enter Create a Sim to make your own unique design! You can experiment with <b><font color='#199C2C'>layers, stamps, stencils</font></b>, and even freehand drawing if you desire!\n\nYou can also offer <b><font color='#199C2C'>dedicated tattoos</font></b>! This option lets you decide who the tattoo should be dedicated to and the type of tattoo it should be. You can dedicate tattoos to family members, lovers, friends, and pets.--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InEP18\UI\Tutorial\EP18_Lesson_Tattooing_Slide3.png">2f7d0004:00000000:9fbd5d8c759554c1</T>
      <T n="text">0xBF2C5A77<!--You can also earn a nice sum of Simoleons from tattooing! Your Sim can <b><font color='#199C2C'>tend</font></b> a Tattoo Table and any nearby Sims who are itching for some new body art will request tattoos and pay for your expertiseâ€”or lack thereof.--></T>
    </U>
